sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Tú (dev)
    participant GH as GitHub Actions
    participant GHRel as Release GitHub
    participant NPM as npm registry
    participant User as Usuario final

    Dev->>GH: Push tag v1.0.0
    GH->>GH: Build en Ubuntu, Windows, Mac
    GH->>GHRel: Sube binarios a la release
    GH->>NPM: Publica paquete npm (sin binarios)
    User->>NPM: npm install -g @astraops/astraops-cli
    NPM->>User: Descarga paquete (scripts)
    User->>GHRel: postinstall.js descarga binario correcto
    User->>User: Usa astraops-cli nativo 